# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-10 22:44

# game/day 5.rpy:85
translate chinese_simplified day05_171b7152:

    # fn "「What to do today?」"
    fn "「今天做什么呢？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:108
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_0bdbefb3:

    # "If I remember right,{p}there's a candy shop here in Minasato."
    "如果我记得没错的话，{p}在水乡村之中有开一家糖果店。"

# game/day 5.rpy:109
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_c663c345:

    # "An old-fashioned, nostalgic, charming,{p}dare I say \"retro\" candy shop."
    "不管是店内店外，都充满了古色古香的气息，{p}不愧是「怀旧」风格的糖果店。"

# game/day 5.rpy:110
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_0e7bef48:

    # "It fits in perfectly with the village's rural image.{p}No matter how you look at it, it's retro.{p}If it were in the city, it'd be pretty popular."
    "这份古朴感完美地适合农村的形象。{p}不管怎么看都非常地复古。{p}如果放到城市去的话肯定会非常受欢迎的吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:111
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_09f9fbe9:

    # "Here, it's the local hangout for the little kids."
    "而且，这里是当地小孩子们聚会的场所。"

# game/day 5.rpy:112
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_b18ae197:

    # "That hasn't changed at all..."
    "就算到了今天也依然没变——"

# game/day 5.rpy:116
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_84ec8840:

    # fn "「Hey guys.」"
    fn "「你好～」"

# game/day 5.rpy:125
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_49c9ce85:

    # ky "「Oh, [fn].」"
    ky "「嗨，{w=.3}博行。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:129
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_1027d59f:

    # ko "「Oh hey!」"
    ko "「啊，{w=.3}YOHOOー！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:133
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_58ef8dba:

    # ka "「Yo.」"
    ka "「唷。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:134
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_c9600c31:

    # "On a whim my destination became the sweet shop.{p}Inside the store were the earlier visitors.{p}Each of them greeted me."
    "临时起意来到了糖果店。{p}当我进入商店时，里面就已经有客人了。{p}而他们每个人现在正跟我打着招呼。"

# game/day 5.rpy:135
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_1eda5a5f:

    # fn "「Huh, so you all came.」"
    fn "「哎呀，你们都来了啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:139
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_0ec3eaa0:

    # ko "「Well, this place has always been our hangout,{p} since way back then.」"
    ko "「嘛，这地方从以前开始{p}就是我们聚会的场所了呀。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:143
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_184a4706:

    # ka "「Sometimes, if we come by here and meet up,{p} we hang around for a bit, you know?」"
    ka "「有时候在附近绕绕时，就会像这样地{p}在这边待一下，你懂吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:147
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_225dceb0:

    # ky "「Anyway, all of us gathering here\n is something like a children's tradition.」"
    ky "「而且，聚集在此应该是水乡村的小孩子们的传统啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:148
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_76070252:

    # fn "「Yeah, I guess so.」"
    fn "「的确是这样没错呢。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:152
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_999acce4:

    # ka "「But lately, there aren't that many kids around.{p} And the ones that usually do come here\n you don't see often anyway.」"
    ka "「但是就我所知村子的小孩子减少了。{p}会来这间店的也已经不常见了。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:156
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_b3aaca0b:

    # ko "「Yeaaah. I came here all right,{p} but there aren't as many customers now\n than there were back then.」"
    ko "「就是说啊ー。{p}我们算很常来的，要是在以前肯定会妨碍到其他客人吧。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:157
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_19714abb:

    # fn "「Still, isn't it thanks to that\n that we all met up together like this?」"
    fn "「嘛，不过拜其所赐，{p}我们才能像这样聚在这里不是吗？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:161
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_b32b9f87:

    # ky "「True, but having high school students like us around\n makes it a little unapproachable for younger kids,{p} don't you think?」"
    ky "「的确啊。{p}一群高中生在里面的话，小孩子们就很难进来了啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:165
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_3aebd0df:

    # ko "「Yeah, Kouya, control yourself!」"
    ko "「就是说啊洸哉。{p}稍微考虑一下别人嘛。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:169
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_29dd6a3c:

    # ka "「What the hell are you saying that to me for?」"
    ka "「为什么要对着我说？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:173
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_bd4d83e3:

    # ko "「Eh? That's 'cause you have bad eyes.{p} They're kinda scary. It always looks like\n you're gonna murder someone! Big bad wolf!」"
    ko "「咦？{p}因为，洸哉的眼神看起来很邪恶啊。{p}很可怕的。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:177
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_230c6913:

    # ka "「First, I'm a husky. Get it right.{p} Second, watch your ass, Kuri,{p} or I'm gonna be shoving my foot up it.」"
    ka "「喂你这家伙。{p}说的事是不是少了什么啊。{p}像是更委婉的表达方式？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:181
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_a4957218:

    # ko "「No, I really...{p} {nw}"
    ko "「不是啊，{w=.3}因为真的很……{p}{nw}」"

# game/day 5.rpy:183
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_22a03031:

    # extend "Ow, owowowowow, Sorry, I-I'll shut up!{p} I-I apologized! Leggo of my head!」"
    extend "好痛，{w=.3}痛痛痛痛痛！{p}对不起，我闭嘴就是了！{p}我道歉啦，放开我的头啦！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:184
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_31cd2071:

    # "As we all joked about,{p}our silly little talk opened up."
    "大家呵呵呵地笑着，{p}因为这种没什么意义的事情而欢笑起来。"

# game/day 5.rpy:185
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_1f8f7ee2:

    # "Things like this were also the same as back then."
    "这种事情，就跟以前一模一样呢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:189
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_34ef1a22:

    # fn "「...Okay then, what should I get?{p} I'm feeling a bit hungry now.」"
    fn "「——那么，要吃什么好呢。{p}正好肚子有点饿了。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:190
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_37c86179:

    # "For a little while after that,{p}we all broke up and looked through the shelves."
    "一会儿过后大家就各自散开，{p}开始挑选起架子上的零食。"

# game/day 5.rpy:191
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_9ef55bc2:

    # "From small snack bags,{p}to candy imitating pork cutlets,{p}the line-up is mostly the same as well."
    "有小包装的零食、{p}或者是炸猪排口味的零食，{p}种类跟以前一样没有太大的变化。"

# game/day 5.rpy:192
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_9142befb:

    # "Everything past here is probably like that too."
    "大概之前也没有什么变化吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:193
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_74047e45:

    # fn "「So many choices, so little time...」"
    fn "「该选什么好呢ー」"

# game/day 5.rpy:194
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_7e3cfb1f:

    # "While I tried to decide,{p}I walked here and there through the shop."
    "我困扰地在店里走来走去。"

# game/day 5.rpy:195
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_4a78b7bf:

    # "And then I noticed that there was also\nmore stuff under the counter by the cash register."
    "然后在柜台的收款机下面，{p}有某个东西引起了我的注意。"

# game/day 5.rpy:196
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_a9387eae:

    # fn "「Woooaaah... that looks awesome...」"
    fn "「哦，果然是这个，不朽的名作。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:197
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_54f85e0e:

    # "As I was muttering something meaningless to myself,{p}I picked one up in my hand."
    "我低喃着连自己都听不太懂的名词，{p}拿起了一个放在了手中。"

# game/day 5.rpy:198
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_edf11415:

    # "Attached to a spherical head of a character,{p}there was a mighty color-changing bag.{p}Inside it, there were fried snacks."
    "那是一个由球形连接的人物，{p}用了色彩鲜艳又会变色的包装。{p}里面是圆柱形的油炸零食。"

# game/day 5.rpy:199
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_554ebfbd:

    # "It's called umaibou."
    "它的名称叫○棒。"

# game/day 5.rpy:200
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_0ac51f50:

    # "It's one my favorites, to be honest."
    "其实我也非常喜欢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:201
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_c1c5ebee:

    # "I haven't had any in a while, come to think of it.{p}In the city, I never really thought\nabout going out to buy some."
    "说起来最近都没有想过这种零食。{p}在城市里不会特地想到，更不用说想买来吃了。"

# game/day 5.rpy:202
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_cf27e686:

    # "All right, I'll go with this then."
    "嗯，就选这个吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:210
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_83c852cf:

    # fn "「Which flavor would be good...?」"
    fn "「要选什么口味好呢……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:214
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_4207b8b4:

    # ko "「It's gotta be salad.」"
    ko "「当然是色拉啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:218
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_220b1722:

    # ky "「No, it should be cheese.」"
    ky "「不对，是起司吧。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:222
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_61452a90:

    # ka "「What are you talking about? Gotta be takoyaki.」"
    ka "「在说什么啊，当然是章鱼烧吧。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:223
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_7a9489fd:

    # fn "「Thanks for the suggestions.{p} But if you want to surprise me,{p} try not to be so obvious about it.」"
    fn "「……先不管你们的意见好不好，{p}拜托不要无声无息地出现在别人背后。{p}会吓死人的啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:224
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_8915dd4c:

    # "Noticing the three of them behind me,{p}I furrowed my brows into a wrinkle as I spoke."
    "我注意到他们三个在我身后，{p}我紧锁眉头说道。"

# game/day 5.rpy:225
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_919b648c:

    # "Maybe I'm too used to the city,{p}but lately I'm having trouble\nnoticing anyone around me."
    "不知道是不是太习惯都市的生活了，{p}最近对人的气息感觉明显弱了很多。{p}莫非在我不知道的时候已经失去了这个技能了吗。"

# game/day 5.rpy:229
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_56c6a3fb:

    # ky "「You've been tamed,\n by the concrete jungle, [fn].」"
    ky "「看来已经在都市丛林中住惯了吶，{w=.3}博行。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:233
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_407154b8:

    # ko "「And you used to be the champ at hide and seek, too.」"
    ko "「在以前玩鬼抓人时可是很厉害的啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:237
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_0bd3bb28:

    # ka "「That's sad. You're not even a shadow\n of who you used to be, huh...」"
    ka "「很可悲啊。{p}已经退步成这样了，{w=.3}吗……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:240
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_4acba668:

    # fn "「Fine, that's enough!{p} Read my mind, why don't you!{p} What is this, a hazing!?」"
    fn "「好了，{w=.3}停！{p}不要随便读人家的内心啦！{p}什么嘛，{w=.3}是在欺负我吗！？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:244
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_3197582b:

    # ky "「Well, let's set that aside.{p} Which one are you getting?{p} Is it going to be cheese, after all?」"
    ky "「好啦这事先放一边。{p}那，{w=.3}你的选择呢？{p}果然是起司对吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:248
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_7d98fcf3:

    # ko "「Didn't we settle on salad?」"
    ko "「已经决定是色拉了对吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:252
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_a6407b3f:

    # ka "「It can't be anything else but takoyaki, right?」"
    ka "「是章鱼烧才对吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:253
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_773bb1cd:

    # fn "「Hmm, let me think...」"
    fn "「唔，这个嘛……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:254
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_fe920ff5:

    # "If I could say something in advance,{p}it feels like a lot of important things\nare being ignored right now."
    "在继续讲下去之前，好像有什么很重要的议题被忽略掉了的感觉，{p}不过应该不是那样吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:255
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_059b8702:

    # "But that's not true at all."
    "——嗯。肯定不是那样。"

# game/day 5.rpy:256
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_493115fe:

    # "...Right, I haven't decided."
    "……嗯，还没有决定呢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:257
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_268f7178:

    # "Still, this choice is pretty hard.{p}Honestly, I like them all.{p}It's hard to say which is better."
    "不过，这个选择还真是困难。{p}说实话每种都喜欢。{p}很难说哪一个比较喜欢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:258
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_c5419d79:

    # "But, if I had to say something,{p}today I'm in the mood for..."
    "但是，真的要我说的话，{p}考虑到今天的心情，果然还是选……"

# game/day 5.rpy:276
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_6f80c47d:

    # fn "「I feel like having salad today.」"
    fn "「今天的心情比较适合色拉。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:282
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_63e2dc69:

    # ko "「Of course, [fn]!{p} You totally get it.」"
    ko "「不错嘛博行！{p}我懂的！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:286
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_264b464e:

    # ky "「...」"
    ky "「…………」"

# game/day 5.rpy:290
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_587d5458:

    # ka "「...」"
    ka "「…………」"

# game/day 5.rpy:291
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_1b038c63:

    # "My agreement had Kounosuke in high spirits.{p}Behind him, Kouya's and Kyouji's shoulders,{p}were slumped and bumping into each other."
    "我和孝之助的意见一致。{p}而在我们背后的洸哉和京慈正在互相槌着肩膀，眼神不断交换着。"

# game/day 5.rpy:292
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_904bab80:

    # "It's a bit of a weird scene."
    "总觉得，这个画面有点诡异。"

# game/day 5.rpy:296
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_887cd0f6:

    # ko "「Just as I thought, that refreshing feeling\n from salad is great!」"
    ko "「果然还是色拉好，有种清爽的感觉真的很棒！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:297
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_8fdc75cd:

    # fn "「Y-yeah...」"
    fn "「是，{w=.3}是啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:298
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_cb23735a:

    # "I do think the taste of salad,{p}doesn't warrant so many words."
    "我的确觉得色拉口味的口感很清爽。"

# game/day 5.rpy:299
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_2d18a28c:

    # "My impression was that\nother tastes were pretty great, too."
    "其他口味不管哪种都有太浓郁的感觉，记得印象中是这样。"

# game/day 5.rpy:300
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_b853d350:

    # "Still, what's up with Kounosuke's cheering?{p}I don't think I'd like to get into the...{p}complexities of his salad fetishes."
    "然而，到底是什么原因让孝之助这么的雀跃。{p}我不认为色拉值得用这么多话来赞美。"

# game/day 5.rpy:301
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_0b8d4692:

    # "If I think about it will I... lose?"
    "感觉去在意的话好像就会输……{w=.3}了？"

# game/day 5.rpy:304
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_95dc5acc:

    # ko "「Okay, I'm gonna buy one too.{p} Wanna eat it together?」"
    ko "「那，我也买一个好了。{p}要一起吃吗？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:305
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_7ba551ee:

    # fn "「Yeah, okay. Wait, hey, Kounosuke!{p} You don't need to... Uh...」"
    fn "「嗯，就一起吃吧。{p}呃，等等孝之助！{p}就算不用拉的我也——」"

# game/day 5.rpy:312
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_ef48e8fc:

    # "Kounosuke paid for both our pieces with 20 yen,{p}then grabbed my hand and walked quickly\nto a table on the oppposite side."
    "孝之助一付完两人份共２０日元，之后，{p}突然抓住我的手，{p}疾步往另一侧的桌子移动。"

# game/day 5.rpy:313
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_fc30067d:

    # "What... Just happened?"
    "到底，发生了什么事情啊。"

# game/day 5.rpy:314
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_37451f50:

    # "Kouya and Kyouji were still bumping shoulders."
    "洸哉和京慈仍站在柜台前面，{p}持续槌着对方的肩膀交换着眼神。"

# game/day 5.rpy:315
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_aa548fe9:

    # "What happened to those two?"
    "就连这两个人也是，到底怎么了啊。"

# game/day 5.rpy:316
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_92bf0f28:

    # "In the end, the day finished\nwithout me really understanding anything."
    "结果，那天解散了之后，我还是不明白发生了什么事情。"

# game/day 5.rpy:317
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_abd29148:

    # "Even when I knew the truth of the matter,{p}I was left in a difficult position."
    "所以当我知道事情的真相时，已经过了一段时间了。"

# game/day 5.rpy:318
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_099f94c7:

    # "According to the sweet shop owner,{p}after Kounosuke left the counter..."
    "根据糖果店老板的证言，{p}在我和孝之助离开柜台之后，"

# game/day 5.rpy:319
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_9710e5b1:

    # "It seemed the two left behind\nhad a conversation somthing like this."
    "被留下的两人似乎是这么交谈的。"

# game/day 5.rpy:325
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_5ca05cb0:

    # ky "「Kouya...」"
    ky "「洸哉……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:329
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_bfa44195:

    # ka "「...What?」"
    ka "「……怎么了？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:333
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_d084d549:

    # ky "「Want to eat together like the losers we are?」"
    ky "「失败组归失败组，还是吃点什么吧。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:337
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_673d9598:

    # ka "「...I guess.」"
    ka "「……也是。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:338
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_a0cd2321:

    # "Back when we were browsing,{p}it seemed the three of them\nhad a bet on what I'd pick."
    "经过调查之后，{p}似乎是他们３人在打赌我到底会选择什么样的口味。"

# game/day 5.rpy:339
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_a39fc553:

    # "After that, the two who lost went up\nand gave Kounosuke two large bottles of soda."
    "在那之后赌输的那两人，{p}交上了要给孝之助的承诺——２公升的宝特瓶饮料。"

# game/day 5.rpy:340
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_salad_1ae183c6:

    # "It doesn't matter to me, but..."
    "虽然没什么关系。"

