translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_0cb2f24a:

    # ky "「If you don't want to, then that's fine.{p} We'll just stop.{w} But if it were Torahiko,\n he'd be in on it...」"
    ky "「你不愿意的话也没办法，还是算了吧。{w}如果是虎彦的话一定敢来的吧……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:593
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_14a93a66:

    # ka "「...Is that a challenge?{p} Fine then, I'm in.」"
    ka "「……你是在挑衅我吗？{p}没问题啊，{w=.3}来就来嘛。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:597
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_a3f49008:

    # ko "「...You guys, you've been saying cheese or takoyaki,{p} but haven't you forgotten the most important one?」"
    ko "「……你们两个刚才开始就争些奶酪啊、{p}章鱼烧的话，把重要的事情都忘记了吗？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:601
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_a2837537:

    # ka "「Huh?」"
    ka "「啊？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:605
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_27b8dfc3:

    # ky "「Hm?」"
    ky "「嗯？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:609
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_ef5164bd:

    # ko "「If it's Umaibou then it has to be salad.{p} If it's not salad, it's pointless,{p} so of course he's going to pick that.」"
    ko "「说起○棒的话当然是色拉味啦？{p}不是色拉味那样的选择项可是没有的。{p}当然，博行也一定会选色拉味的啦。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:613
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_5a82ccb8:

    # ky "「I say cheese.{p} Kouya says takoyaki.{p} And Kounosuke says salad. All good?」"
    ky "「那我选奶酪味。{p}洸哉是章鱼烧。{p}孝之助选色拉就行了？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:617
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_034897cd:

    # ko "「Ah, I hope I get two bottles of orange juice.」"
    ko "「啊，{w=.3}奖品的宝特瓶饮料希望是橙汁啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:621
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_730e8c11:

    # ka "「You've think you've won!?」"
    ka "「你已经觉得自己赢了吗！？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:625
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_a121d54e:

    # ko "「Of course.」"
    ko "「那当然了！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:629
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_6a59d17a:

    # ky "「Well, that doesn't really matter.{p} The rule says it can be anything.{p} The point is to encourage yourself to want to win.」"
    ky "「嘛，那个怎么样都好啦。{p}规则是什么都可以。{p}总之为了获胜，自己做推荐也是可以的。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:634
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_264e10ac:

    # ky "「All right, go!」"
    ky "「那么，开始——」"

# game/day 5.rpy:650
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_245dc036:

    # ka "「...And that's what happened.」"
    ka "「——总之，{w=.3}就是这样了。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:654
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_2e156eb1:

    # ky "「I was thinking of just teasing Kouya at first,{p} but it went awry somewhere along the line...」"
    ky "「一开始只是为了戏弄一下洸哉才这么做的，{p}不过，从途中开始就意外地向{p}其他的方向发展了……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:658
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_8d235f66:

    # ko "「It's not like you had any ill will right?」"
    ko "「并没有什么坏心思的啦。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:659
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_cfb43626:

    # fn "「Yeah, I get it, I get it.」"
    fn "「嗯嗯，{w=.3}我明白了。{p}非常彻底地了解了呢。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:660
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_79d6468d:

    # "...It's a bit stupid."
    "虽然明白了，{p}不过也是白费工夫。"

# game/day 5.rpy:661
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_d883d532:

    # "It's that, what's the word I'm looking for?\nI forgot for a second, umm..."
    "那个是，{w=.3}用来表达这种感情的词语。{p}有点不记得了，{p}那个……"

# game/day 5.rpy:666
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_88d03df9:

    # "Ah,{w=.3} \"dumb.\"{p}Lately my vocabulary has been getting worse, damn."
    "啊，{w=.3}「吃惊」。{p}最近总是忘记事情很为难啊，真是的。"

# game/day 5.rpy:667
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_294fd2d5:

    # "At any rate, what happened with these three?{p}They aren't blaming anyone,\nso this ending is a bit anticlimatic."
    "既然如此，这三个人怎么办呢。{p}就这样谁也不责备地结束的话，{p}实在是有些无趣啊。"

# game/day 5.rpy:668
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_b4e6b1e3:

    # "Should I demand an apology and compensation?"
    "是不是可以要求一些作为赔罪的赔偿呢？"

# game/day 5.rpy:669
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_92ddc51e:

    # "...I know, I just thought up of a good game."
    "——对了，想到了一个很好的惩罚游戏。"

# game/day 5.rpy:670
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_c0b1c0f3:

    # fn "「For now, I'm really shocked,{p} but I haven't said just how shocked I am.」"
    fn "「总之我很吃惊，{p}现在吃惊得连吃惊这样的词都说不出来。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:671
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_d6a625f5:

    # "From just one word from me,{p}the three of them hung their head in shame."
    "我说的每一个字，{p}让那三人都丢脸地垂下了头。"

# game/day 5.rpy:672
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_eb523e41:

    # "Geez, for keeping a secret from me\nI'm gonna say this."
    "总之因为他们瞒着我，{p}我就要这么说了。"

# game/day 5.rpy:673
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_bbaef1c8:

    # fn "「For now, you can make it up to me\n by getting me two large sodas.」"
    fn "「那么作为补偿的东西就是2L装的宝特瓶饮料没问题吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:679
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_581b824b:

    # "All Three" "「Huh?」"
    # [旧版翻译]
    "三人异口同声：「诶？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:680
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_70abbc0c:

    # fn "「It was going to be the prize anyway, right?{p}As punishment for keeping a secret from me,{p}go get them for me.」"
    fn "「反正是预定的奖品对吧？{p}作为瞒着我下赌注的惩罚，{p}奖品就贡献给我吧。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:681
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_be98948e:

    # "Everyone was surprised by the announcement."
    "听了我对处罚的说明，大家都露出惊讶的表情。"

# game/day 5.rpy:682
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_878d49e5:

    # "But I'm not going to stop here.{p}There's still more."
    "但是我的处罚到这里还没有结束。{p}还有后续的。"

# game/day 5.rpy:683
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_4125a245:

    # "And with a smile, I informed them of it."
    "带着微笑的表情，我宣布处罚的后续。"

# game/day 5.rpy:687
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_3b01934b:

    # fn "「Now, how about we all drink together?」"
    fn "「然后，大家一起来喝吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:688
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_6030ee56:

    # "Since that was so tasty, it should be fun."
    "因为饮料很美味，应该会很快乐吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:689
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_66707bb7:

    # "It'd be best for us to do something together."
    "果然，不管做什么还是大家一起最好了。"

# game/day 5.rpy:693
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_4e3f9e89:

    # ka "「[fn]...」"
    ka "「博行……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:694
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_137c81f9:

    # fn "「Come on, I'm going to go buy them now.{p} Let's go already.」"
    fn "「那么现在就去买。{p}快点出发吧！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:698
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_e9e13cc6:

    # ky "「Whoa!?」"
    ky "「啊！？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:703
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_5cd51e75:

    # ko "「Hey, [fn], don't push! That's dangerous!」"
    ko "「等下，博行不要推我啦，很危险的！」"

# game/day 5.rpy:709
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_1ce6faa6:

    # "I pushed everyone from behind,\nand we all left the shop."
    "推着大家的背，我们离开了店。"

# game/day 5.rpy:710
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_d947c5fb:

    # "The gloomy mood hanging over us was blown away.{p}With that, it was just like always."
    "从刚才开始笼罩我们的紧张气氛一扫而光。{p}这样之后，又一如往常。"

# game/day 5.rpy:718
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_c3d1d411:

    # ky "「Seriously, we're no match for [fn].」"
    ky "「真是完全敌不过博行啊。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:722
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_c8173b14:

    # ka "「If anyone's as crazy,{p} I'd think that Torahiko is the only one\n who could even compare to him.」"
    ka "「啊，说起来从以前开始，{p}就只有虎彦能跟得上他{p}这种奇怪的调子。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:726
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_93ef1954:

    # ko "「You said it.」"
    ko "「嗯，确实是这样。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:727
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_a624bc2b:

    # fn "「What!?{p} And after I've shown you a bit of slack!?」"
    fn "「什么嘛！{p}好不容易做和善这种事！？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:728
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_b19a160c:

    # "Here or there, it's the same as always.{p}We'd laugh over the simple things."
    "不管是现在还是以前，都是一样的。{p}我们为了简单的事情欢笑着，一起嬉闹。"

# game/day 5.rpy:729
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_da77765f:

    # "For the punishment games,{p}it always would be something fun."
    "甚至是惩罚游戏，{p}都能够愉快地渡过。"

# game/day 5.rpy:730
translate chinese_simplified kouya05_takoyaki_c2ad1126:

    # "That's because we'd all be laughing,{p}as we all walk alongside each other."
    "因为大家肩并着肩走着，{p}一起欢笑着。"

# game/day 5.rpy:749
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_90eb05b3:

    # who "「Yo, what are you up to?」"
    who "「哟，在干什么呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:750
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_855977ed:

    # fn "「Hey, Tatsu-nii. Done with work already?」"
    fn "「呀，辰兄，工作已经结束了吗？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:751
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_8bbd83cb:

    # "Looking back over my shoulder,\nTatsu-nii was leaning out the window of his run-down\nlight truck, waving at me."
    "转头看去，辰兄正从那破破烂烂的小型卡车里探出身子冲我挥手。"

# game/day 5.rpy:752
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_9654193a:

    # "The racket of the engine got louder as\nhe pulled the truck up alongside me."
    "辰兄的小型卡车伴着咯吱咯吱的噪音迎面驶来，然后停在我旁边"

# game/day 5.rpy:756
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_d2cdab0f:

    # ta "「Yep, just finished now.{p} After this, I'm gonna take a bath and have a drink.」"
    ta "「是啊，刚刚结束呢。{p}等下先洗个澡再配着下酒菜喝点小酒吧」"

# game/day 5.rpy:760
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_82c63273:

    # fn "「Just how old are you, again...?」"
    fn "「辰兄是几岁来着……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:761
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_ab042600:

    # ta "「Gahaha! Hell if I know.」"
    ta "「噶哈哈，不知道呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:765
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_c7a682a4:

    # ta "「I'm going home right now,\n do you want me to give you a lift to somewhere?」"
    ta "「我现在正要回去，要不顺便也送你回去？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:777
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_778d1713:

    # fn "「Sorry, I have stuff I need to do.」"
    fn "「抱歉，我有点东西要买顺便还要去做点事」"

# game/day 5.rpy:781
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_4a0d2379:

    # ta "「Oh. I guess it can't be helped, then.」"
    ta "「这样啊，那就没办法了」"

# game/day 5.rpy:782
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_76965866:

    # fn "「Instead of saying that,\n you could just wait until I was finished.」"
    fn "「要是辰兄说无论如何也想送我回去的话，等我这边的事结束了再走也行」"

# game/day 5.rpy:783
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_0688d48e:

    # ta "「No way. I wanna go home already.」"
    ta "「才不要呢，我可是想快点回去的呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:787
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_31e780e2:

    # fn "「You're so cold.」"
    fn "「切，真冷淡呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:788
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_0a094d19:

    # ta "「Don't say that so shamelessly.」"
    ta "「这叫厚脸皮」"

# game/day 5.rpy:789
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_d77b2897:

    # fn "「Haha, well, I'm heading off then. Bye, Tatsu-nii.」"
    fn "「哈哈，那我也差不多该走了。ByeBye 辰兄」"

# game/day 5.rpy:790
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_4a5f9bd8:

    # ta "「Yeah. Take care, [fn].」"
    ta "「喔，回去路上小心点」"

# game/day 5.rpy:791
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_d1157f3f:

    # fn "「You too.」"
    fn "「你才是」"

# game/day 5.rpy:797
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_bd7a5111:

    # "No matter which way you look at it...{p}Tatsu-nii's the one who needs to take care."
    "要说哪一边的话……确实是辰兄需要注意点才是呢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:798
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_f5dcaac8:

    # "He's kind of careless, and his driving's crazy.{p}But that's just like him."
    "糊里糊涂的，开车也好像很"厉害"呢。\n嘛——这样才像是辰兄的风格。"

# game/day 5.rpy:799
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_busy_6b36696f:

    # "I should finish up here and head home, too."
    "我也做完事回去吧。"

# game/day 5.rpy:808
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_b40c3204:

    # fn "「Uhh... Is your driving okay?」"
    fn "「诶……开车没问题么？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:809
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_01a5f990:

    # "I think everyone has warned\nme about Tatsu-nii's driving,\nand it worries me a bit..."
    "说真的，因为我从大家那里听到辰兄开车的技术，有点不放心呢……"

# game/day 5.rpy:813
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_b428b272:

    # ta "「What, are you questioning my driving technique?」"
    ta "「什么啊，在怀疑本大人的开车技术吗」"

# game/day 5.rpy:814
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_51467db2:

    # fn "「No, it's not that...{p} It's just you're super aggressive, Tatsu-nii.」"
    fn "「不，并不是那个意思啦……\n你看辰兄平时都很积极的嘛」"

# game/day 5.rpy:818
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_c9ed538b:

    # ta "「If you've got something to say, then spit it out.\n Someone probably told you that my driving's scary.{p} And here I was looking forward to driving you, too...」"
    ta "「有想说的话就说清楚啊，反正就是从谁那里听到我开车很恐怖什么的吧。\n难得说想送你一趟……」"

# game/day 5.rpy:819
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_02058c44:

    # fn "「Sorry, I've got errands to do.\n I need to do some shopping, too.」"
    fn "「抱歉我有要事要做。而且也想去买东西。」"

# game/day 5.rpy:820
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_2736ceab:

    # ta "「Okay, okay, I got it.\n If you've got errands, then there's no helping things.{p} I don't think you want a ride afterwards.{w=.3} Later.」"
    ta "「知道了知道了，有要事的话就没办法了。\n以后说想坐上来什么的我可不管了。{w=.3}就这样了」"

# game/day 5.rpy:825
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_36611dab:

    # "Aah, now I've done it. I wonder if he's mad?{p}But it really does seem scary, and I do have errands,\nso I can't really get around it.{w} {nw}"
    "啊——啊，走掉了，应该没生气吧。\n不过好像真的很恐怖，而且我也有事要干，没办法的吧"

# game/day 5.rpy:827
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_22dcbbf6:

    # extend "{w=.5}{nw}"
    extend "{w=.5}{nw}"

# game/day 5.rpy:829
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_9614f1e4:

    # extend "{w=1}{nw}"
    extend "{w=1}{nw}"

# game/day 5.rpy:832
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_22dcbbf6_1:

    # extend "{w=.5}{nw}"
    extend "{w=.5}{nw}"

# game/day 5.rpy:834
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_a03a0117:

    # fn "「Eeeh???」"
    fn "「诶诶诶？？？？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:838
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_14b6593c:

    # "All of a sudden, there was a braking sound,\nand I turned my head in surprise.\nOn the other side of the road, smoke was billowing."
    "听到身后传来了急刹车的声音，我惊讶地回过头看，道路的那一边出现团团的黑烟飘了起来。"

# game/day 5.rpy:839
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_avoid_b28c8e97:

    # fn "「That can't be Tatsu-nii.{p} But the light truck is the Midoriya Gro...{p} It flipped over... Tatsu-nii?{w} Tatsu-nii...?」"
    fn "「应该不会是辰兄吧。\n不过，那辆轻卡车是翠屋组的……。\n翻过来了……辰兄？辰兄——」"

# game/day 5.rpy:848
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_a12aef02:

    # fn "「Thanks, that'd be great!」"
    fn "「帮大忙了，那就不客气让你送我一趟了」"

# game/day 5.rpy:854
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_b4a5827d:

    # ta "「Oh, that's a special place.」"
    ta "「哦，那里是特等席哦」"

# game/day 5.rpy:858
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_d5f6ab17:

    # ta "「I don't let just anyone sit next to me.」"
    ta "「因为我的旁边大家都不会坐呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:859
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_85a1cbec:

    # "Come to think of it..."
    "说起来……"

# game/day 5.rpy:860
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_35f93464:

    # "I think just about everyone has said something\nor other about riding in Tatsu-nii's car."
    "辰兄开的车不要坐，好像大家都这样说过呢。"

# game/day 5.rpy:861
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_41d4d32e:

    # fn "「It's just until I finish my errands.\n This is really good timing.」"
    fn "「正好我做完事想着回去呢。\n真是Nice timing呢」"

# game/day 5.rpy:865
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_62cfc6fc:

    # ta "「Yeah, it is.」"
    ta "「喔，那真是太好了」"

# game/day 5.rpy:866
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_a2717ecf:

    # fn "「So you did get your licence.\n Is your driving all right?」"
    fn "「诶，考到驾照了呢。开车没问题吧？」"

# game/day 5.rpy:870
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_182eb6e6:

    # ta "「Of course. I use this car every day for work.{p} All right, let's head off.」"
    ta "「当然了。因为每天工作都有在开呢。\n那么出发吧」"

# game/day 5.rpy:874
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_13d39065:

    # "As Tatsu-nii said that,\none of his tires gave a loud groan,\nand kicked up a large dust cloud.{w} {nw}"
    "辰兄说着便让轻卡车的轮胎发出呜呜的声音，卷起大量沙尘后急速前进着。"

# game/day 5.rpy:876
translate chinese_simplified tatsuki05_accept_22dcbbf6:

    # extend "{w=.5}{nw}"
    extend "{w=.5}{nw}"

